{"tid":1667062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]唔該大家改一改唔好慣咗用某d字詞！","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:28:41.000Z","uid":210682,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"761e9c8dce414fd1f67bffceaf8da72e4479668f","tid":1667062,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"你講句說話嘅時候，入面d詞語有可能反映某種價值觀/暗示，從而影響成句句子嘅框架，例如冇型中抬高咗敵人、潛意識認同咗對家套思想，以下係一d例子:<br />\n<br />\n1.乜 sir <br />\n<br />\n&quot;sir&quot;喺英文語系入面代表社會地位高尚嘅人，例如爵士，佢地叫Sir Alex Ferguson。而就算用本地觀念，你叫佢做乜sir已經有under佢嘅感覺！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 國產<br />\n<br />\n除非你好想自己係中國人，否則應指明係中國產<br />\n<br />\n3. 返大陸<br />\n<br />\n&quot;返&quot;有回家嘅意思，正確應係&quot;去中國&quot;"},{"pid":"0d685e84783ac3b9373611dcd029456ce496272f","tid":1667062,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"3494bbc46b8838b8ffef3d890059e48273dff15f","tid":1667062,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ef60ccd38a7b3df3c957fd4749f7e33f5e4b6d","tid":1667062,"uid":183890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:12:46.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"df92df58ff1b61248d37edeb24ad53db0d27ccc2","tid":1667062,"uid":135114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761e9c8dce414fd1f67bffceaf8da72e4479668f","tid":1667062,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"你講句說話嘅時候，入面d詞語有可能反映某種價值觀/暗示，從而影響成句句子嘅框架，例如冇型中抬高咗敵人、潛意識認同咗對家套思想，以下係一d例子:<br />\n<br />\n1.乜 sir <br />\n<br />\n&quot;sir&quot;喺英文語系入面代表社會地位高尚嘅人，例如爵士，佢地叫Sir Alex Ferguson。而就算用本地觀念，你叫佢做乜sir已經有under佢嘅感覺！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 國產<br />\n<br />\n除非你好想自己係中國人，否則應指明係中國產<br />\n<br />\n3. 返大陸<br />\n<br />\n&quot;返&quot;有回家嘅意思，正確應係&quot;去中國&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:20:02.000Z","msg":"返大陸通常係鬧人<br />\n或者中國香港人自己用"},{"pid":"83f68359bcaff2b6ac539bbea547bb02d96cd771","tid":1667062,"uid":53808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"黑警<br />\n<br />\n嗰班著制服有武器嘅人 冇number冇證<br />\n都唔知咩人嚟<br />\n唔好再叫黑警 <br />\n你覺得佢係咩就叫咩 我覺得佢哋係殺人犯/強姦犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b277c3d48e3d3f68209aa53049917ca448d0400","tid":1667062,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"d84835142ffb03da9a238ed3edeecdad7e6eee72","tid":1667062,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"1f16cf81308d3d8d9d4b50d942ff55c0b1503516","tid":1667062,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626085b6e581c0776540c39a6f59fdcdc82ea5fa","tid":1667062,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"叫佢阿生好啦<br />\nsir佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有&quot;警嫂&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講撚咗好多次<br />\n&quot;嫂&quot; 即係佢兄你弟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48260fe3ff42c3504b810270ebdf0b88e1aa2934","tid":1667062,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"我會話返香港同返台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946ab81fe187a98d7855782b2ea8fb3c761324b7","tid":1667062,"uid":263234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"係囉 成日都聽到人地話返大陸,大陸又唔係你屋企 點解用&quot;返&quot;<br />\n應該用&quot;去&quot;"}]}